---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const lang = 'en';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" lang={lang}>
  <div class="pt-32 pb-20 px-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-muted mb-12">Last updated: May 2026</p>

    <div class="space-y-8 text-muted leading-relaxed">
      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">1. Who We Are</h2>
        <p>Henna By Hanazz is a henna artistry service based in Barcelona, Spain. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal data when you use our website or services.</p>
        <p class="mt-2">Contact: <a href="mailto:info@smgtec.es" class="text-gold underline">info@smgtec.es</a></p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">2. Data We Collect</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Booking information:</strong> name, email address, phone number, and any special requests you provide when booking a session.</li>
          <li><strong>Newsletter signup:</strong> email address when you subscribe to receive our henna aftercare guide or marketing updates.</li>
          <li><strong>Usage data:</strong> anonymized analytics via Google Analytics and Facebook Pixel (with your consent only).</li>
          <li><strong>Payment data:</strong> payment details are processed by Stripe — we never store your credit card information.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">3. Legal Basis for Processing</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Contract performance:</strong> processing your booking and sending confirmation emails.</li>
          <li><strong>Consent:</strong> newsletter emails, analytics and tracking cookies (you can withdraw anytime).</li>
          <li><strong>Legitimate interest:</strong> improving our services and website experience.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">4. Data Retention</h2>
        <p>We retain booking data for 2 years after your last appointment. Newsletter subscriber data is retained until you unsubscribe. Analytics data is retained for 14 months.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">5. Third-Party Processors</h2>
        <p>We share data with these trusted processors under strict data processing agreements:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 mt-2">
          <li><strong>Supabase</strong> (USA) — database hosting and authentication</li>
          <li><strong>Stripe</strong> (USA) — payment processing</li>
          <li><strong>Resend</strong> (USA) — transactional email delivery</li>
          <li><strong>Google Analytics</strong> (USA) — website analytics (with consent)</li>
          <li><strong>Meta/Facebook</strong> (USA) — advertising analytics (with consent)</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-2">All transfers to third countries are covered by the EU-US Data Privacy Framework or Standard Contractual Clauses.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">6. Your Rights (ARCO / GDPR)</h2>
        <p>Under Spanish law (LOPDGDD) and the GDPR, you have the right to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 mt-2">
          <li><strong>Access</strong> — request a copy of your personal data</li>
          <li><strong>Rectification</strong> — correct inaccurate data</li>
          <li><strong>Erasure</strong> — request deletion of your data ("right to be forgotten")</li>
          <li><strong>Restriction</strong> — limit how we use your data</li>
          <li><strong>Portability</strong> — receive your data in a machine-readable format</li>
          <li><strong>Objection</strong> — object to processing based on legitimate interest</li>
          <li><strong>Withdraw consent</strong> — at any time, without affecting the lawfulness of prior processing</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3">To exercise these rights, email us at <a href="mailto:info@smgtec.es" class="text-gold underline">info@smgtec.es</a>. We will respond within 30 days.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">7. Complaints</h2>
        <p>If you believe we have not handled your data correctly, you have the right to lodge a complaint with the Spanish Data Protection Agency (AEPD) at <a href="https://www.aepd.es" class="text-gold underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">www.aepd.es</a>.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-text mb-3">8. Updates</h2>
        <p>We may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
